# A tracked TEXT file silently classified as BINARY is UNDIFFABLE, so no edit to it is
# ever reviewable. That happened once to a skill read by a dozen agent clones and nobody
# noticed for weeks. Skills are read by many and reviewed by few — they must stay
# diffable from the first commit.
*.md   text diff
*.py   text diff
*.sh   text diff
*.toml text diff
*.json text diff
